1
00:01:30,930 --> 00:01:34,970
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:41,509 --> 00:01:43,000
I once thought my life

3
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,509
would always be bright and radiant,

4
00:01:45,509 --> 00:01:46,840
smooth and effortless.

5
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:49,150
But then,

6
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:51,120
at some unexpected turn,

7
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,000
fate nudged the clock off course

8
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,740
and changed my direction.

9
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,430
The world is fickle,

10
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,850
and losing control is the norm.

11
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:03,150
From that moment on, my world

12
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,090
became dim and chaotic.

13
00:02:07,690 --> 00:02:09,490
If everything could start over,

14
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,580
would I be able to have a perfect life?

15
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,080
Don't forget—

16
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,240
every gift from fate

17
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,500
comes with a price tag.

18
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,560
And are you truly sure

19
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,820
you want to start over?

20
00:02:18,570 --> 00:02:21,860
[Episode 1]
[Do you really want to start over?]

21
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:28,210
[New Year, 2026]

22
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,079
Xiaolan.

23
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,520
Xiaolan.

24
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,650
Wake up, Xiaolan.

25
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:53,670
You're awake.

26
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,190
Who are you?

27
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,960
I'm your mother.

28
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,960
Psychopath.

29
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:04,750
Xiaolan.

30
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,360
Don't scare me.

31
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:08,680
Are you okay?

32
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,080
Don't move around.

33
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,740
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

34
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,680
Don't touch that wound.

35
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,530
Xia Xiaolan!

36
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,560
Why don't you just die?

37
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:18,950
Xiaolan?

38
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:26,040
Xiaolan.

39
00:04:35,090 --> 00:04:36,620
What the hell is this place?

40
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,400
Mr. Wang.

41
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:44,290
Look at the contract you signed off on!

42
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,330
Xia Xiaolan.

43
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,240
How dare you talk about promotion?

44
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,180
Because of you,

45
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,640
our company has to pay
a huge compensation!

46
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:51,800
What?

47
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:52,330
Come on.

48
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,070
Take a look at the contract yourself.

49
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:56,190
See what the joint-liability clause says!

50
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,830
It was you who signed this contract,
wasn't it?

51
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,230
All our company's losses

52
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,890
will be borne by you alone!

53
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,970
You can leave now

54
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,040
and wait to be sued!

55
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,040
Mr. Wang, I didn't...

56
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:04,630
Get lost!

57
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,240
Mr. Wang...

58
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:06,770
Get lost!

59
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,430
If you can't pay the compensation,

60
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,690
get ready to go to jail!

61
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:33,270
Get up. Stop pretending.

62
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,040
Xiaolan.

63
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:35,890
Xiaolan?

64
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:36,690
Be quiet.

65
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:42,510
Our Ziyu is a college student.

66
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,920
She's going to move to the city
in the future.

67
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,560
How could Jianhua possibly
take a liking to you?

68
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,270
She got in!

69
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,310
Yeah, she got in. She got in.

70
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:51,390
What kind of sin
has our Xia family committed

71
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,040
to end up getting
a daughter-in-law like you?

72
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,070
Giving birth to a daughter

73
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:55,750
who has no shame, either!

74
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:57,870
Get out of my way!

75
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,480
What are you doing?

76
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,310
Move aside!

77
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,160
I'll beat her to death!

78
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,960
Xia, don't...

79
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:07,930
Xiaolan!

80
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,630
This has nothing to do with us.

81
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,840
She crashed into it herself.

82
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,040
Xiaolan!

83
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,480
This has nothing to do with us.

84
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,590
She crashed into it herself.

85
00:06:15,590 --> 00:06:17,160
She's just pretending, you know?

86
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,040
She's just faking it.

87
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,750
Quite convincing, huh?

88
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:25,270
Could it be that I've transmigrated

89
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,240
and become another Xia Xiaolan?

90
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,270
Wait.

91
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,480
Is this for real?

92
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,580
She's completely shameless,

93
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,680
messing around with that scoundrel

94
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,510
and even seducing her sister's man.

95
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,950
Auntie, don't get angry with her.

96
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:41,150
She's really going to be the death of me.

97
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:45,830
Xiaolan.

98
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:46,750
Xiaolan!

99
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,430
Xiaolan, you can't get out there!

100
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,800
I'm so mad.

101
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,159
What's going on?

102
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,430
Isn't that the shameless

103
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:53,480
Xia Xiaolan?

104
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:55,380
Why is she coming out now?

105
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:57,800
I've become someone else,

106
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:01,340
yet all I face are still
accusations and gossip.

107
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,760
What kind of fate is this?

108
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,530
I did once hope to be
the center of attention.

109
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,120
But definitely not like this.

110
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,720
Xia Xiaolan.

111
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,190
You actually dare to show your face?

112
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,650
Grandmother... And Aunt?

113
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:18,190
Aren't you ashamed enough?

114
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,000
You jinx.

115
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,560
Didn't you say you want to die?

116
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,760
So why don't you do it?

117
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:24,390
Why don't you just go ahead and do it?

118
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,190
You...

119
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:28,430
Blocking me from hitting her, huh?

120
00:07:28,430 --> 00:07:29,270
Not fighting back?

121
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,480
Mother! Mother, I'm begging you!

122
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,190
She's even kneeling down.

123
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,430
Please spare Xiaolan
and give her a way out.

124
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:33,830
I'm begging you, Mother.

125
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:34,830
Whether it's a dead end or a way out,

126
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,030
she chose it herself.

127
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,120
She disgraced herself!

128
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:41,080
Why should I be the one
to give her a way out?

129
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,270
Exactly!

130
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,310
Even Hongxia has been affected by her.

131
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:44,840
Hongxia!

132
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,870
Why are you still standing there?

133
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:46,620
Don't you feel embarrassed?

134
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:47,820
Take the kids inside.

135
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,020
Shameless.

136
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,240
Look.

137
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,070
Xia Xiaolan, look around you.

138
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:53,870
Just look.

139
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,360
Look around—every man and woman,

140
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,390
old and young in this whole village

141
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:59,159
thinks you're a disgrace!

142
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:01,160
A bunch of haters.

143
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,630
One

144
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,610
only knows how to chase men...

145
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,240
Mother, please stop hitting Xiaolan.

146
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:06,560
I'm begging you.

147
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,720
And the other can't even bear a son.

148
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,830
If she had died earlier...

149
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:11,920
This old hag just won't stop.

150
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,040
It would have been doing a good deed

151
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,870
for the Xia family, you know?

152
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:17,510
You old hag.

153
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,830
Watch your mouth.

154
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:19,750
That'd be the only good deed
you can do for yourself.

155
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:22,080
Mother, she actually dares to insult you!

156
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,830
What are you all making a fuss about?

157
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,270
Watching this family drama
is great fun, huh?

158
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,530
Are you even involved?

159
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,600
Do you even know what actually happened?

160
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,870
Throwing dirt at others

161
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:31,310
with your foul mouths—

162
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,289
you find it entertaining, huh?

163
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,450
Who was it just now?

164
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:35,320
You.

165
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:36,549
And you, right?

166
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,600
Come on, say it again.

167
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,400
Let me hear it.

168
00:08:39,669 --> 00:08:40,270
What's wrong?

169
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:40,669
Xiaolan...

170
00:08:40,669 --> 00:08:41,799
Too scared to speak?

171
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,159
Not so brave now, huh?

172
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:44,630
Xia Xiaolan!

173
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,480
So the Xia household

174
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,320
can't contain you anymore?

175
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,630
Mother, she's too big for us now.

176
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,320
Too big for us!

177
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,360
She's out of control. So out of control.

178
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,610
Your pathetic little household

179
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:54,240
truly can't contain a great deity like me.

180
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,120
You're all crazy.

181
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,650
-How dare you?
-Xiaolan...

182
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,030
Mother, she's leaving!

183
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,440
Jingui, go after her!

184
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:00,500
Xiaolan.

185
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,630
Xiaolan!

186
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,440
What are you doing?

187
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,670
I'll go! I'll go!

188
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:08,000
Hurry up and go after her!

189
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,630
Xiaolan!

190
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,150
Come back here, Xiaolan!

191
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,030
Xiaolan!

192
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,080
Stop right there!

193
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,670
Xiaolan, stop running!

194
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:15,200
I said stop!

195
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,070
Come back with me, okay?

196
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:16,510
Jingui.

197
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,600
Where do you think you're going?

198
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,930
Xiaolan, come back now!

199
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,130
Come back with me, okay? Stop running.

200
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:23,190
-Run faster, Jingui!
-Xiaolan!

201
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:24,390
Xiaolan!

202
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,120
Xia Xiaolan!

203
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,450
Isn't that Xia Xiaolan?

204
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,240
Xiaolan!

205
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,790
This little troublemaker!

206
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,080
Let's see how far you can run!

207
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,960
Jingui,

208
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,550
don't just pretend to help, alright?

209
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,880
Mind your own business!

210
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:45,550
I'm too old to run fast.

211
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:53,910
Cheng. Cheng.

212
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,100
Look. What's going on over there?

213
00:09:57,690 --> 00:10:00,350
Looks like they're bullying
those two up ahead.

214
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,870
Wait for them to pass,

215
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,070
and then stop the car.

216
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:37,960
Jingui!

217
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,530
-Run faster!
-Xiaolan!

218
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,550
Stop running!

219
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,440
What kind of driving is this? Move!

220
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,750
Do you even know how to drive?

221
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:44,840
You're blocking the way!

222
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,510
What's going on?

223
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,150
Get out of the way!

224
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:46,870
Everyone.

225
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,360
Excuse us. Excuse us.

226
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,240
Our car broke down.

227
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:49,910
We might need

228
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:50,670
to trouble you all

229
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:51,800
to help push the car.

230
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,550
Xiaolan. Xiaolan.

231
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,920
I really can't run anymore.

232
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,170
Come back with me

233
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,360
and apologize to your grandmother,

234
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,020
then everything will be fine.

235
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,630
Wei.

236
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,360
Wei. Wei.

237
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,360
Move aside! We have important business.

238
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,550
Where are you going, aunties?

239
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:05,630
Who are you calling "aunties"?

240
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,600
Bro, come on.

241
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,570
Have a cigarette.

242
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:08,550
These are cigarettes from the city.

243
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,120
Really good stuff.

244
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,670
Try one.

245
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:10,730
Have a try. Come on.

246
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,390
Here, try one, come on.

247
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,240
Xia Xiaolan!

248
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,510
Easy, easy, easy.

249
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,030
Liu Fen!

250
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:15,960
What's going on?

251
00:11:16,070 --> 00:11:17,000
Calm down. Calm down.

252
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,630
Get back here!

253
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,240
There are groceries in the car.

254
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,000
Do you want some?

255
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,530
Let's go.

256
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,840
-Let's go, Xiaolan...
-Xiaolan!

257
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,270
Fen!

258
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:25,670
Yong?

259
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:26,790
Why are you here?

260
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:27,720
What's going on?

261
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,080
I came as soon as I heard about Xiaolan.

262
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,940
What happened?

263
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,700
How did you two end up here?

264
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,910
Her grandmother was trying to beat her.

265
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:37,030
Xia Xiaolan, you shameless girl!

266
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:37,960
You loose woman!

267
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,680
Zhang Cui!

268
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,760
Shut your filthy mouths!

269
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:43,080
You think the Liu family
has no one to stand up for them, huh?

270
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,240
Stop yelling!
There are so many people around.

271
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,790
I'll kill you both!

272
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:45,390
I'm warning you,

273
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:46,480
this is the Xia family's business!

274
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,150
It's not your place to speak, Liu Yong!

275
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:49,390
Harmony brings wealth, remember?

276
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:50,910
Zhang Cui, Wang Jingui!

277
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,510
Yong!

278
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:53,310
Look, I, Liu Yong, am right here!

279
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,980
Who do you think you're cursing at?

280
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,150
Xiaolan is still injured.

281
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,080
Let's leave now.

282
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:57,630
Let's go.

283
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,390
Let's go, Yong.

284
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:58,920
Let's go.

285
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,030
Sis. Sis.

286
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,700
Come back here.

287
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:02,600
Xia Xiaolan!

288
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:03,870
Be good and get on the bike.

289
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,600
Xiaolan, get on.

290
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,120
Sit in the front.

291
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,270
No one will dare bully you.

292
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:06,730
Come on.

293
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,270
Get on.

294
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,360
No big deal. No big deal.

295
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:11,480
Shoes!

296
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,640
Hold on tight.

297
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,120
Just you wait!

298
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,230
Enough. Stop yelling.

299
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:17,440
Why are you stopping me?

300
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,170
Xia Xiaolan!

301
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,200
Just you wait!

302
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,390
We'll definitely bring you back!

303
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,630
They just let those two leave like that?

304
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:22,320
Yeah.

305
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,320
I'm so mad.

306
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:25,410
They can run but they cannot hide.

307
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,610
I've transmigrated

308
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:46,000
all the way back to 1983

309
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,960
and become Xia Xiaolan,
carrying a terrible reputation

310
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,870
and a failed suicide attempt.

311
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,630
Everything here is strange to me.

312
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:57,510
The only thing I know right now is that

313
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:59,240
behind me are my uncle Liu Yong,

314
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,790
my mother Liu Fen,

315
00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:05,120
and my aunt, Li Fengmei.

316
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,150
Xiaolan.

317
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,360
Does it hurt?

318
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,960
I've always said

319
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:15,360
there's not a decent person
in the Xia family.

320
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,390
Where is that good-for-nothing Xia Dajun?

321
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,050
Where is he?

322
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,510
His daughter is in such trouble

323
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:20,220
and he doesn't even dare make a peep!

324
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:20,930
A grown man

325
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,620
without an ounce of backbone.

326
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,360
All day long, he just

327
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,390
listens to his brothers

328
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,200
and his mother

329
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,150
talking nonsense.

330
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:26,870
Turns out the whole family

331
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:27,670
has been bullying Fen

332
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:28,630
and Xiaolan all long.

333
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:30,480
They'll be struck by lightning for this!

334
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,910
Alright, enough. Stop shouting.

335
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,770
Go make dinner.

336
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:33,960
What's this?

337
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,370
You bought this?

338
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,410
Sweet noodles? You...

339
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,600
Our homemade noodles are so much better.

340
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,720
Tastier and cheaper.

341
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,890
What a waste of money.

342
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:43,600
What do you mean "a waste of money"?

343
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,440
I bought these for the Xia family.

344
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,840
If I had known their family was like that,

345
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,480
I'd rather feed this to the dogs
than give it to them!

346
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,000
Bro,

347
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,440
so we're the dogs you feed now?

348
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,570
Just go make dinner.

349
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,480
Fengmei, I'll go with you.

350
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:53,910
No, no.

351
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,260
Just sit here and rest.

352
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,400
It'll be ready soon.

353
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:58,320
Son.

354
00:13:58,670 --> 00:14:00,270
Take Xiaolan inside to play.

355
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:03,280
Xiaolan, let's go play horsey!

356
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:23,630
Charge!

357
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,000
I need to talk to you, Fen.

358
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:40,750
Charge!

359
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,150
Xiaolan.

360
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,650
Does your head hurt?

361
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,930
I'll blow on it for you.

362
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:56,350
Come here.

363
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,670
I want to ask you some questions.

364
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,120
What's your name?

365
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,320
Tao.

366
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,080
Tao.

367
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:05,750
So how old are you this year, Tao?

368
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:06,670
Seven.

369
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,320
Seven.

370
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:09,950
So how old am I, little...

371
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,700
How old am I this year, Tao?

372
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:17,120
You were 17 last year,

373
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,580
so you're 18 this year.

374
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:25,910
And what does your father do?

375
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,050
He works in the city

376
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,440
as a bricklayer.

377
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,360
A bricklayer...

378
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,690
Xiaolan, have some too.

379
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:37,320
I don't want any.

380
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:38,270
Go play.

381
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,000
With those people in the village

382
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,200
and all their gossip,

383
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:50,020
Xiaolan doesn't want to stay at home.

384
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,510
It's fine for her to be away
for a few days.

385
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:53,840
But what if Dajun comes back?

386
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:54,650
What then?

387
00:15:54,870 --> 00:15:57,270
If he really wanted to come back,
wouldn't he have already?

388
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,320
It must be his mother

389
00:15:58,320 --> 00:16:00,050
stopping him from coming back.

390
00:16:00,870 --> 00:16:02,200
She's not stopping him.

391
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:03,870
She just said

392
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,550
if Dajun comes back,

393
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,510
they won't get

394
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:09,110
the riverbank repair money.

395
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,480
Fen.

396
00:16:12,270 --> 00:16:13,550
Your husband Xia Dajun—

397
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:14,440
has he ever given you

398
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,770
a penny of his earnings?

399
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:16,550
All these years,

400
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:17,910
haven't they all gone to his mother

401
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:18,870
to support that Xia Ziyu

402
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:19,870
and their family?

403
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:22,720
Mother said

404
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,910
it's not easy for our family
to have a college student.

405
00:16:24,910 --> 00:16:26,910
We should be thrifty at home
and spend liberally while travelling.

406
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:28,790
My goodness, Fen.

407
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:29,600
They've been bullying you

408
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,440
like this,

409
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:32,370
yet you're still defending them?

410
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,510
I know your temperament.

411
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:35,630
But at this point,

412
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:36,510
you can't

413
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,440
be so weak anymore.

414
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,480
Not only are you suffering,

415
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:40,140
but Xiaolan is suffering too.

416
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,360
Your decision now

417
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,720
affects Xiaolan's

418
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,840
future happiness.

419
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,790
She's already 18 years old.

420
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,200
Is there anyone in the Xia family

421
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,600
who stands up for you two?

422
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:49,270
Is there anyone

423
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,630
who speaks up for Xiaolan?

424
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:52,690
They'd rather drive her to her death!

425
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,510
-Come on, let's eat.
-Alright.

426
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:12,970
Come on.

427
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:13,770
Xiaolan.

428
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,270
Fen,

429
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,410
dinner's ready!

430
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:17,400
Coming.

431
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,440
What's that you've been holding all day?

432
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:22,480
W-What is it?

433
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,339
What's inside?

434
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,750
Well, you know, Xiaolan is injured.

435
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,880
So I thought I'd make
something nourishing for her.

436
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,080
Steamed egg custard.

437
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:30,160
Come on.

438
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,070
Here.

439
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,800
Eat up, Xiaolan, come on.

440
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,270
Come on, eat up.

441
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:35,920
The noodles are getting soggy.

442
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,960
Come on, hurry up.

443
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,760
I'm sorry,

444
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,210
but I'm not your daughter.

445
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:51,440
Xiaolan.

446
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:54,290
Why aren't you eating?

447
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:01,640
Let's...

448
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:03,680
Let's all eat.

449
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,110
Thank you all.

450
00:18:11,350 --> 00:18:12,210
Eat up. Come on.

451
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,070
Eat up.

452
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:18,270
You won't get full just eating this.

453
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:18,680
Have more noodles.

454
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,000
No.

455
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,670
I don't want any vinegar.

456
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:37,400
Xiaolan,

457
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,450
sleep on this side later, okay?

458
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,390
You'll be sleeping here too?

459
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:48,550
Well...

460
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,720
I can go sleep in the main room.

461
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,320
There's not even a bed there.

462
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:55,640
Just sleep here.

463
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,640
Together is fine.

464
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,310
It's really hard.

465
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:24,000
How about I go get you

466
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:24,880
another quilt?

467
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,240
No, don't bother.

468
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,210
Alright.

469
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:29,950
I'll turn off the light then.

470
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,680
They've gone to bed?

471
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:47,310
I'm worried about Xiaolan's head injury.

472
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:49,440
Could it leave her with some problems?

473
00:19:49,790 --> 00:19:50,880
Did you notice how she was talking
during the day?

474
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:51,750
Weird, right?

475
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:53,070
And she was not as close to us

476
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,400
as she usually is.

477
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,440
I've noticed that too.

478
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:58,680
What a shame.

479
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:01,240
I want the two of them

480
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:03,350
to stay with us a bit longer.

481
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:06,200
Since this matter hasn't been resolved,

482
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:07,790
if they go back to the Xia family,

483
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,520
they'll be bullied even worse.

484
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:10,930
Is that okay?

485
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:14,830
Well, she's your sister after all.

486
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:16,890
If we don't take care of her, who will?

487
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:19,210
Alright, let's go to sleep.

488
00:20:21,050 --> 00:20:22,450
Once things settle down,

489
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,640
I'll go out and start earning money
right away.

490
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,070
Don't push yourself too hard.

491
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:26,830
I'm fine.

492
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,960
With those two staying with us,

493
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,890
you're the one who'll have it hard.

494
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:43,350
Xiaolan.

495
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:45,390
You'll live here from now on.

496
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:50,850
Ask your parents to come.

497
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:52,250
Ask your parents to come.

498
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,550
I just remembered,

499
00:20:53,550 --> 00:20:54,880
you don't have parents.

500
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:00,550
Coffee.

501
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,070
Thanks.

502
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:03,790
Thanks.

503
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,030
Xia.

504
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,930
Where's the coffee I asked for?

505
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,240
You can have this one.

506
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:09,920
Xia.

507
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,480
Mr. Li needs this by ten.

508
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,340
Take care of it.

509
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,310
Print two copies of this

510
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:14,570
and give them to Mr. Li.

511
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,070
Xia.

512
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:22,800
Finish this and you can go home.

513
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:26,240
Okay.

514
00:21:27,980 --> 00:21:29,240
You signed this contract, didn't you?

515
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,640
All our company's losses

516
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,290
will be borne by you alone!

517
00:21:32,510 --> 00:21:34,240
If you can't pay compensation,

518
00:21:34,270 --> 00:21:35,530
get ready to go to jail!

519
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:41,310
My phone.

520
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:24,590
Smell it.

521
00:22:25,270 --> 00:22:26,530
Doesn't it smell good?

522
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:28,060
Yes.

523
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:28,920
It does.

524
00:22:29,580 --> 00:22:30,840
Let me apply it for you.

525
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,270
Now you look beautiful.

526
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:43,010
I woke up on the Xia family's bed.

527
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:46,640
Maybe that's the portal
I transmigrated through.

528
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,600
If I lie back down...

529
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:50,830
Let's make something

530
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:52,230
for Xiaolan to eat later.

531
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,880
How about I make spicy soup?

532
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,550
Doesn't she love

533
00:23:54,550 --> 00:23:55,970
the spicy soup I make for her the most?

534
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:56,590
With a splash of vinegar—

535
00:23:56,590 --> 00:23:57,650
it's so delicious.

536
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,000
But she said last night

537
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,030
that she doesn't like vinegar.

538
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:02,030
That's not right.

539
00:24:02,110 --> 00:24:03,270
Didn't Xiaolan use to

540
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:04,530
love vinegar the most?

541
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,880
Breakfast's ready!

542
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:16,440
Tao.

543
00:24:16,460 --> 00:24:17,990
Hurry up and eat breakfast.

544
00:24:18,620 --> 00:24:19,380
Come here.

545
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,790
Those little hands of yours.

546
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:23,120
Look how dirty they are.

547
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:25,080
Here, freshly steamed buns.

548
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,110
Eat while they're warm.

549
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:27,000
Eat while they're still warm.

550
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,000
Smells so good.

551
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:28,960
Here.

552
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:30,830
Be careful, it's hot.

553
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,070
Why don't you ever learn?

554
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,000
Use chopsticks.

555
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,340
Here, hold them properly.

556
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,220
Auntie's steamed buns

557
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:42,480
are better than Mom's.

558
00:24:42,770 --> 00:24:43,510
You ungrateful boy.

559
00:24:43,510 --> 00:24:45,830
Forgetting your mother
when Auntie's around, huh?

560
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:47,680
Eat more if you like them.

561
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:48,940
Our Tao will grow tall.

562
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:51,110
Growing smart is what matters.

563
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:55,730
Xiaolan.

564
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:56,560
You're up.

565
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,200
Come on.

566
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:58,480
Come eat breakfast.

567
00:24:59,070 --> 00:24:59,640
Come on.

568
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:01,480
We made your favorite spicy soup.

569
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,480
Come on, Xiaolan.

570
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,350
Come on.

571
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:05,510
Hurry up.

572
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,070
Xiaolan.

573
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:19,550
Your hair looks pretty.

574
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:21,510
Here.

575
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:24,000
More chili for our Xiaolan.

576
00:25:24,550 --> 00:25:26,010
Xiaolan loves spicy food.

577
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,000
Eat while it's still warm.

578
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,270
I made this especially for you.

579
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:30,070
Smell it. Doesn't it smell good?

580
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:36,720
Eat decently.

581
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:38,350
Could you not make so much noise?

582
00:25:38,350 --> 00:25:40,350
No one's fighting with you for food.

583
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:42,200
Eat up, Xiaolan.

584
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:44,800
It's okay.

585
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:46,130
I'm not hungry.

586
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:47,910
I'll just have a steamed bun.

587
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,720
You can't think of doing anything foolish!

588
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,270
Let go of me!

589
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:40,880
Everything will pass!

590
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:41,270
Let me go!

591
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,400
You can't try to kill yourself!

592
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,110
I wasn't thinking of anything foolish.

593
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:46,040
You almost pushed me down, though.

594
00:26:46,550 --> 00:26:47,610
It's just I've been

595
00:26:48,270 --> 00:26:49,400
following you for a while...

596
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,800
Why are you following me?

597
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:54,380
I was worried
you might do something stupid.

598
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,140
I saw ducks down there,

599
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:58,920
so I was wondering
if there were any duck eggs.

600
00:26:58,920 --> 00:26:59,980
Stop following me.

601
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,880
Watch your step, alright?

602
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:13,320
My goodness.

603
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,240
Xiaolan.

604
00:27:14,710 --> 00:27:15,770
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

605
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,960
If you want to do something, let me know.

606
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:20,490
You... What duck eggs
were you talking about?

607
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:22,920
Are they over there?

608
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,320
Wait here. I'll go check.

609
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:35,790
Xiaolan!

610
00:27:36,510 --> 00:27:37,770
There really are some!

611
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:40,090
Xiaolan?

612
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,110
Xiaolan!

613
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:45,160
I'm sorry.

614
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,420
You love your daughter very much,

615
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:48,280
but I'm not her.

616
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:49,440
I have to go back.

617
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:53,790
Make way! Make way!

618
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,200
Zhang.

619
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,570
Isn't this Xiaolan?

620
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,000
Are you going back to Dahe Village?

621
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,060
Let's go together.

622
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:07,200
Come on, get on.

623
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,440
This can be exchanged for some money.

624
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:10,750
Come on.

625
00:28:10,750 --> 00:28:11,210
Come on.

626
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,030
Xiaolan.

627
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,680
Why aren't you getting on?

628
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:15,510
If you walk back,

629
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:16,680
you won't make it before dark.

630
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,740
Hurry up and get on.

631
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:19,300
Be careful.

632
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,400
Sit here, sit here.

633
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,400
Come on, sit here.

634
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:22,680
Sit tight.

635
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,170
Alright.

636
00:28:24,570 --> 00:28:25,850
We had a great

637
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,110
radish harvest this year.

638
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:28,110
Hitting the road!

639
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,550
You two, stop messing around.
Go play outside.

640
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:37,200
So noisy.

641
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,350
Grandma, tea.

642
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,440
Oh my goodness!
Are you trying to scald me?

643
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,640
Are you okay, Mother?

644
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:43,640
Hongxia.

645
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,370
Take these two outside to play.

646
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,110
Look at you, so clumsy.

647
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,160
Seriously.

648
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:00,730
Our Ziyu is so much better.

649
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,590
Now that Ziyu isn't home,

650
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:03,480
let me tell you something.

651
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,510
You both have to listen to me.

652
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,000
Otherwise, I won't play with you.

653
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:07,130
Behave yourselves.

654
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:48,080
Since you brought me here,

655
00:29:48,230 --> 00:29:49,230
take me back.

656
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,690
This should be about right.

657
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:11,680
Goodbye, 1983.

658
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,280
You two, go sleep inside.

659
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,000
Go on.

660
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:22,000
Mother.

661
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:24,740
I don't want to work at the snack shop.

662
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,000
How tiring that must be.

663
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,460
Then what do you want to do?

664
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:29,240
You're not cut out for school.

665
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,960
Are you in a hurry to get married?

666
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,960
That Wang boy

667
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,090
hasn't come to see you for days.

668
00:30:33,090 --> 00:30:35,020
Isn't that because of Xia Xiaolan?

669
00:30:35,620 --> 00:30:37,950
Stop saying it's about Xia Xiaolan, okay?

670
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:38,750
Don't you know

671
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:39,920
what's really going on with yourself?

672
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,960
Wasn't that just an excuse for others?

673
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:42,960
With your stubborn attitude,

674
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,360
who would dare marry you?

675
00:30:44,770 --> 00:30:45,640
I get mad whenever I see you.

676
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,570
Take this. Don't just stand there.

677
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:19,880
Why are you back?

678
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:22,770
Who are you?

679
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:23,750
Who am I?

680
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:25,830
Did that fall mess up your brain?

681
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:27,710
Mother!

682
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:29,240
Don't shout.

683
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,840
I came back to get something.

684
00:31:33,110 --> 00:31:34,370
Want to see what I have?

685
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:36,510
Come on.

686
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,440
A dress?

687
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:57,320
You like my dress, don't you?

688
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:59,680
Take it. Be quiet.

689
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:04,640
So pretty.

690
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:09,030
Mother! Grandma!

691
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:10,160
Xia Xiaolan is leaving again!

692
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,270
-Mother...
-Stop shouting.

693
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:11,750
Shut up.

694
00:32:12,750 --> 00:32:13,920
Mother! Grandma!

695
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:15,440
Xia Xiaolan is back,

696
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,990
but she's leaving again!

697
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:17,480
Mother!

698
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:17,790
Stop there!

699
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:18,960
Jingui, help hold Mother up!

700
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,110
You stop right there!

701
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:20,570
Mother.

702
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,520
Xia Xiaolan, oh Xia Xiaolan.

703
00:32:24,550 --> 00:32:25,960
You think you can leave whenever you want

704
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,890
and come back whenever you please?

705
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:29,650
What do you think this place is,

706
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,960
a marketplace?

707
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:33,270
Yeah.

708
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:34,680
Do you have a problem with that?

709
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,590
I do have a problem!

710
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:37,210
Mother.

711
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:39,590
Let me make this clear

712
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:40,320
to you today:

713
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:44,030
if you dare step out that door today,

714
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:46,400
I'll make sure you never set your foot

715
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,160
back through it again!

716
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:51,300
Try me if you don't believe it!

717
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:55,750
Mother.

718
00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:56,960
Calm down. Calm down.

719
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,400
What are you trying to do?

720
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,310
What are you trying to do?

721
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:01,110
Why are you holding the knife?

722
00:33:01,110 --> 00:33:01,830
Put it down! Put it down!

723
00:33:01,830 --> 00:33:02,880
What are you trying to do?

724
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,280
Don't do anything crazy!

725
00:33:04,510 --> 00:33:04,970
Wait...

726
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,640
Don't worry.

727
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,570
I'll never come back

728
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:18,380
to this darn place ever again.

729
00:33:22,590 --> 00:33:23,830
She's completely out of control.

730
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:24,510
I'm telling you, Mother,

731
00:33:24,510 --> 00:33:25,770
it's all because of Liu Fen's spoiling.

732
00:33:25,770 --> 00:33:28,940
If you don't come back, then don't.

733
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:32,030
Why did you have to ruin my vegetables?

734
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,200
Don't just stand there!

735
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,270
Hurry up and clean this up!

736
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:35,000
My poor vegetables!

737
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:37,200
My poor baby vegetables!

738
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:37,920
Look at you.

739
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,450
You couldn't even stop her.

740
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:49,850
You're so greedy, little glutton.

741
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:50,730
Alright.

742
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:52,920
Fen.

743
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:53,680
Yong.

744
00:33:55,270 --> 00:33:56,350
Is Xiaolan back yet?

745
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:57,000
No.

746
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:57,600
She's not.

747
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:01,480
I've searched the whole village,
but I couldn't find her.

748
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,550
Looks like I have to go to the Xia family
to check.

749
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,110
I'll go with you.

750
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:05,070
Don't.

751
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:07,380
Just stay here and wait for me.

752
00:34:08,550 --> 00:34:10,670
Xiaolan, where have you been?

753
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:14,590
I went to get my things
from the Xia family.

754
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:15,920
I couldn't let them keep my stuff.

755
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,630
You did the right thing.

756
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:17,880
They shouldn't have any of it.

757
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:18,840
Come on. I'm just glad you're back.

758
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:19,300
Come on.

759
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,510
Let's eat. Let's eat.

760
00:34:20,510 --> 00:34:21,840
We're glad you're back.

761
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:22,570
Give it to me.

762
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,000
Come on.

763
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:31,480
I was about to go look for you,

764
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:34,480
but your uncle was worried
we might miss each other.

765
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,840
I thought since you like duck eggs,

766
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:37,370
I picked a few extra for you,

767
00:34:37,590 --> 00:34:39,920
and I've been waiting for you
to come back.

768
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:44,710
Thank you.

769
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:48,190
Let's eat.

770
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:48,900
Come on.

771
00:34:51,030 --> 00:34:52,090
Come on, let's eat.

772
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:54,210
Xiaolan, you must be starving.

773
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,960
1, 2, 3.

774
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,960
It's so pretty.

775
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:00,880
Isn't it?

776
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:01,630
Yes, it is.

777
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,320
I noticed

778
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,230
how you couldn't take your eyes off this.

779
00:35:04,230 --> 00:35:04,960
Do you like it?

780
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:05,550
I do.

781
00:35:05,670 --> 00:35:06,800
Thank you, Mom.

782
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,410
Alright.

783
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:12,280
Let's go spin around.

784
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:14,230
Be careful. Don't drop it.

785
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,360
Move a bit, will you?

786
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:22,230
Move a bit!

787
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,920
Why are you abandoning me too?

788
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:33,660
If you were still here,

789
00:35:36,470 --> 00:35:37,230
would I not

790
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:38,630
have to struggle so hard?

791
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,370
The alarm clock!

792
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:13,810
It must have been the alarm clock
that sent me through time.

793
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,010
Alarm clock.

794
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,910
Do we have an alarm clock?

795
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,400
In the village, once the roosters crow,

796
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,070
it's morning.

797
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:23,470
Who needs an alarm clock?

798
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:26,810
Xiaolan.

799
00:36:27,510 --> 00:36:28,480
If you want an alarm clock,

800
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:30,340
I'll go to town and buy one for you.

801
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,250
Look, Fen

802
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,510
collected so many duck eggs.

803
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:40,310
How can we possibly eat them all?

804
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:40,840
I'm thinking

805
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:41,670
maybe we should go to town

806
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:42,710
and sell them.

807
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:45,150
I'll go.

808
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:48,070
This is China National Radio.

809
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:49,850
Dear listeners,

810
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:52,510
here are a few news briefs.

811
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,960
According to Xinhua News Agency,

812
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:55,760
with rural areas advancing

813
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:58,360
the production responsibility system,

814
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:01,480
this year's summer grain harvest
has been another bumper crop.

815
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:03,510
Farmers are enthusiastically
selling their grain,

816
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:05,440
market supply is becoming stable,

817
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,670
and in many places,
communes and production teams

818
00:37:07,670 --> 00:37:08,550
are developing diversified operations
according to local conditions.

819
00:37:08,550 --> 00:37:10,110
Would you like a bowl of noodles?

820
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,810
So this is what a county town

821
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,240
looked like in the 1980s.

822
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:15,080
It's actually quite lively.

823
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:17,960
This market has abundant goods,

824
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:18,880
so selling here

825
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:20,190
would definitely not be competitive.

826
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:20,840
I need to find

827
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:22,760
a place where demand exceeds supply

828
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,590
to sell you

829
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:24,550
in exchange for an alarm clock.

830
00:37:24,550 --> 00:37:25,960
Chicken eggs, want some?

831
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:27,110
Fresh and big chicken eggs!

832
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:27,880
Come on.

833
00:37:28,230 --> 00:37:29,280
Come on, kid.

834
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,340
Come and take a look.

835
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,670
Come check the eggs out.

836
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:32,570
Come on.

837
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,800
Laid by free-range hens at home.

838
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:37,670
Come check out the eggs.

839
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:39,030
I'll come back for them later.

840
00:37:39,030 --> 00:37:39,760
Romaine lettuce.

841
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,280
Potatoes! Potatoes!

842
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,210
Come take a look!

843
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,550
Come check them out!

844
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:44,280
Garlic, 5 cents per catty.

845
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:46,400
Come on, chicken eggs, very nutritious.

846
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,400
Fresh big chicken eggs.

847
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,440
Come on! Buy some!

848
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:50,480
I'll take the potatoes at
5 cents per catty.

849
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:52,670
Check this out, fresh wild duck eggs!

850
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,510
Wild duck eggs, very delicious!

851
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:56,670
How could wild duck eggs be
as tasty as chicken eggs?

852
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:58,110
These are laid by hens

853
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:58,920
raised at home.

854
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,110
Come check them out.

855
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,840
But my eggs are bigger!

856
00:38:02,230 --> 00:38:04,150
But my chicken eggs are fresher!

857
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:05,770
But my eggs are bigger!

858
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:07,280
Free-range chickens!

859
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,150
Eggs laid by free-range hens!

860
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:11,480
Come on, buddy. Take a look at these eggs!

861
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,920
Come on, check out these eggs!

862
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,360
Alright.

863
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:13,880
Come on, young lady.

864
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,740
Time for some marketing tactics.

865
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:17,630
The red and green ones are the same price.

866
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:18,110
Young lady.

867
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:19,570
Come check out these eggs.

868
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:21,230
Mister.

869
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:23,400
I'm selling duck eggs over there.

870
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:24,630
Could I get some green onions on credit?

871
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:26,030
I'll pay you back after I sell my eggs.

872
00:38:26,030 --> 00:38:27,150
Sure, no problem.

873
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:28,590
Thank you so much.

874
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,510
Fresh wild duck eggs!

875
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:32,360
Check it out!

876
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:34,150
The more you buy, the better deal you get!

877
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:36,410
Buy 21 eggs and get green onions for free!

878
00:38:36,590 --> 00:38:37,520
Come take a look!

879
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:38,670
Fresh wild duck eggs.

880
00:38:38,670 --> 00:38:39,480
Really good stuff.

881
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,440
I know these are duck eggs,

882
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,440
but what does this mean?

883
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,840
This is green onion.

884
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:43,920
If you buy more than 20 eggs,

885
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,880
I'll give you green onions for free.

886
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:47,070
It's really delicious
stir-frying green onions with duck eggs.

887
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:47,960
If you think it's too many

888
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:48,670
and you can't finish them all,

889
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:49,880
you can also make salted duck eggs
at home.

890
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,590
If you buy more than 20,
it'll be 0.11 yuan each.

891
00:38:51,590 --> 00:38:52,400
Okay, I'll take 21 then.

892
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:53,480
Sure, no problem.

893
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:55,670
Look at these green onions.

894
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:56,960
I'll give you a big bunch for free.

895
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,280
Here are the green onions for you.

896
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,480
-Alright.
-Here you are.

897
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,320
Thank you. Thank you.

898
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:01,440
Fresh wild duck eggs!

899
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,070
The more you buy, the better deal you get!

900
00:39:03,070 --> 00:39:05,400
You can stir-fry them
with green onions at home.

901
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,400
Sure, no problem.

902
00:39:07,230 --> 00:39:08,630
Alright, I have plenty.
Enough for everyone.

903
00:39:08,630 --> 00:39:09,550
One at a time, please.

904
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:11,000
Okay, thank you.

905
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:11,710
I'll take 2.

906
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:13,550
Here, put them in your bag.

907
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:14,880
Just a moment, let me get your change.

908
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,480
Here you go.

909
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:18,800
Here. Here.

910
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,110
Finally my turn.

911
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:23,190
Here.

912
00:39:23,590 --> 00:39:24,840
This is my last bunch of green onions,

913
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:25,630
and I'll give them all to you.

914
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:26,110
Thanks.

915
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,670
All sold out?

916
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:29,710
Yes, mister.

917
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:31,600
Let me pay you back first.

918
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:32,550
Alright, alright.

919
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:33,550
Thank you so much.

920
00:39:33,630 --> 00:39:34,000
Don't mention it.

921
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:34,510
If you hadn't

922
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,190
let me sell on credit earlier,

923
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:35,800
I wouldn't have been able

924
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:37,070
to sell these eggs so quickly.

925
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:38,320
I saved these 4 duck eggs for you.

926
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:38,800
Please try them.

927
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:39,150
Okay.

928
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:39,920
Stir-fry them with the green onions.

929
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,030
It's really delicious.

930
00:39:41,030 --> 00:39:41,440
Alright.

931
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:41,880
Thank you.

932
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:42,510
I'll definitely try it.

933
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:43,590
Come back tomorrow, young lady.

934
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,000
Sure.

935
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:50,880
Miss,

936
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,510
would you like a bowl of noodles?

937
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,670
Check out this soup

938
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:54,480
I made from big bones.

939
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,230
It's really delicious.

940
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:56,030
Boss, here.

941
00:39:57,110 --> 00:39:57,610
Alright.

942
00:39:57,610 --> 00:39:58,920
Here's the food coupon.

943
00:39:58,920 --> 00:39:59,450
Alright.

944
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:00,430
And the money.

945
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,070
What's wrong?

946
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,480
Didn't bring any food coupons?

947
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,140
No worries.

948
00:40:06,230 --> 00:40:07,150
Money is fine.

949
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:08,790
It's 2 dimes per bowl.

950
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:09,550
Okay,

951
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,320
I'll have one bowl then.

952
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:10,800
Sure.

953
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,840
Find a place to sit,

954
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:13,110
and I'll cook the noodles for you.

955
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:14,280
Cooking noodles.

956
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:35,800
9.22 yuan.

957
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,970
Should be enough to buy an alarm clock.

958
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:44,880
Cheng,

959
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,630
let's buy some buns to eat on the way.

960
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:57,160
Let's have noodles.

961
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:01,400
Ma'am,

962
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:02,840
two bowls of noodles, please.

963
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,280
Sure.

964
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:04,460
Find a place to sit.

965
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:09,030
Cheng,

966
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:11,800
is that the girl we ran into yesterday?

967
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:25,920
Stop staring, Cheng.

968
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,780
She's leaving.

969
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:30,510
What are you looking at?

970
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:32,310
Never seen a pretty girl before?

971
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,440
Why are you pretending now?

972
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:36,640
You've been sneaking glances for ages.

973
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,230
I wasn't sneaking glances.

974
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:39,430
I was looking openly.

975
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:44,150
What's so interesting about me?

976
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,150
You look special.

977
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,820
You don't seem like
you're from around here.

978
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,320
It's you.

979
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,670
You drove past yesterday and kicked up
a cloud of dust on me,

980
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:53,330
didn't you?

981
00:41:54,190 --> 00:41:54,880
Well, um...

982
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:56,150
I was the one driving yesterday.

983
00:41:56,150 --> 00:41:56,950
Sorry, sorry.

984
00:41:58,630 --> 00:42:00,760
But it was fortunate that we happened to
pass by

985
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:01,800
and helped you out of that situation.

986
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:04,460
I guess that evens things out between us,
right?

987
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:05,840
Can I get to know you?

988
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:08,480
Since we're even now,

989
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:10,480
there's really no need for that, right?

990
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,150
Ma'am,

991
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:13,360
is there a watch shop nearby?

992
00:42:13,630 --> 00:42:14,430
Yes, there is.

993
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,340
Just go straight down this street

994
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:18,550
and through Anping Alley,
and you'll find it.

995
00:42:18,550 --> 00:42:19,480
Okay, thank you.

996
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:20,770
You're welcome.

997
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:23,310
Excuse me, could you please move aside?

998
00:42:33,710 --> 00:42:34,280
Cheng,

999
00:42:36,070 --> 00:42:37,710
not a good start, huh?

1000
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,010
Xia Xiaolan.

1001
00:43:04,670 --> 00:43:06,000
Sold all your duck eggs?

1002
00:43:06,630 --> 00:43:07,890
Didn't save any for us?

1003
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:12,000
You bitch! How dare you kick me!

1004
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:12,550
Let me go!

1005
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:12,960
Get over here!

1006
00:43:12,960 --> 00:43:14,550
You think we don't know
what you're really like?

1007
00:43:14,550 --> 00:43:15,150
Let me go!

1008
00:43:15,510 --> 00:43:16,000
Help!

1009
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:16,670
Didn't you have a great time

1010
00:43:16,670 --> 00:43:17,670
with Zhang Erlai?

1011
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:19,670
-Let me go!
-Why pretend to be chaste now?
